<p itemprop="description"><b>创作立场声明：</b>时间仓促，简单开箱</p><p itemprop="description"><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimSun; font-size: 16px;">购买理由</span><br/></p><p itemprop="description">    去年鞋王倒钩实在是太火了，所以今年<a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/727/" data-brandid="727" target="_blank">耐克</a>为了恰饭，就出了一个差不多配色的大货量版本AJ1黑<a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/55884/" data-brandid="55884" target="_blank">摩卡</a>，样子确实是有咖啡的样子，大家嘴上说着不要，后面肯定还是真香的~<img alt="又蹭上了....AJ1小倒钩-黑摩卡开箱" src="https://res.smzdm.com/images/emotions/152.gif" class="face" /> 昨天线下中了一双，所以今天就抓紧给大家开箱来了~</p><h2 id="cl_0">外观展示</h2><p itemprop="description">      鞋盒是正常的AJ1高帮的黑红鞋盒，<a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/184933/" data-brandid="184933" target="_blank">简约</a>又简单，从鞋底的标签可以看出，鞋面也不是全真皮的，还有有一人造皮存在。</p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7ovxw4/pic_2/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202011/20/5fb710c73e7ea6476.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" alt="鞋盒"/></a>鞋盒</span></p><p itemprop="description">    鞋子本身还是很好看的，黑脚趾的配色，后跟处简单是褐色麂皮，摸起来很顺，有一点点的刷色效果，鞋头和侧面白色的荔枝皮纹路不是很大，所以看起来也比较舒服<img alt="又蹭上了....AJ1小倒钩-黑摩卡开箱" src="https://res.smzdm.com/images/emotions/189.gif" class="face" /> </p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7ovxw4/pic_3/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202011/20/5fb710c87524d5106.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" alt="鞋子本体"/></a>鞋子本体</span></p><p itemprop="description">    正面看过去黑<a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/41211/" data-brandid="41211" target="_blank">白熊</a>猫的样子~</p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7ovxw4/pic_4/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202011/20/5fb710c99bcfa1164.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" alt="正视"/></a>正视</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/