<p itemprop="description">感觉是故意硬钢，PALACE在Supreme与STONE ISLAND合作同时，发布了与<a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/7855/" data-brandid="7855" target="_blank">MOSCHINO</a>的联名系列。</p><p itemprop="description">19日我们已经发布了这条消息： </p><span class="embed-card  main-site res_smzdm" style=""><span class="embed-card-logo"><a target="_blank" onclick="sensors.track('AddToCart', {'article_title':'就是搞笑：PALACE x MOSCHINO男女服饰装备微信上就能买','article_id':'a99wk8p7','brand':'MOSCHINO/ 莫斯奇诺','mall_name':'无','channel':'news','go_path':'无','channel_id':'6','cate_level1':'服饰鞋包'});if(typeof gtmWikiCard != 'undefined'){gtmWikiCard({'id':'2757501','card_type':''});}" class="" href="https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5gzx3o" ><img ol  alt="就是搞笑：PALACE x MOSCHINO男女服饰装备" class="" src="https://a.zdmimg.com/202011/19/5fb63c9c56e823145.jpg_a200.jpg" ></a></span><span class="embed-card-info"><a target="_blank" onclick="sensors.track('AddToCart', {'article_title':'就是搞笑：PALACE x MOSCHINO男女服饰装备微信上就能买','article_id':'a99wk8p7','brand':'MOSCHINO/ 莫斯奇诺','mall_name':'无','channel':'news','go_path':'无','channel_id':'6','cate_level1':'服饰鞋包'});if(typeof gtmWikiCard != 'undefined'){gtmWikiCard({'id':'2757501','card_type':''});}" class="" href="https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5gzx3o" ><span class="card-name">Supreme x STONE ISLAND联名男士冬装</span></a><span class="card-abstract">小编注：此篇文章来自#原创新人#激励计划，新人发文前三篇文章，篇篇额外奖励50金币。参加超级新人计划活动，新人发文即可瓜分10万金币，周边好礼达标就有，邀新任务奖励无上限，点击查看活动详情近期想和大家从街头文化角度聊聊羽绒服和迷彩，先按下不表，我们先把11月19日，对，就是这一天必须同步给大家的消息</span><span class="card-controls"><a target="_blank" onclick="sensors.track('AddToCart', {'article_title':'就是搞笑：PALACE x MOSCHINO男女服饰装备微信上就能买','article_id':'a99wk8p7','brand':'MOSCHINO/ 莫斯奇诺','mall_name':'无','channel':'news','go_path':'无','channel_id':'6','cate_level1':'服饰鞋包'});gtmAddToCart({'name':'Supreme x STONE ISLAND联名男士冬装','id':'2757501' , 'price':'无','brand':'无' ,'mall':'无', 'category':'无/无/无/无','metric1':'无','dimension10':'smzdm.com','dimension9':'news','dimension11':'无','dimension20':'无',