<p itemprop="description"><br></p><p itemprop="description">写给那些不愿意baidu的人，也是为了方便自己以后设置，如果能帮到你就收藏一下。</p><h2 id="cl_0">本次相关硬件&amp;软件<br/></h2><p itemprop="description"><a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/1681/" data-brandid="1681" target="_blank">华硕</a>（<a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/1681/" data-brandid="1681" target="_blank">ASUS</a>）RT-AC85P无线<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/luyouqi/" target="_blank">路由器</a></p><p itemprop="description">J1900绿牌NAS刷的<a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/3063/" data-brandid="3063" target="_blank">威联通</a>系统</p><p itemprop="description">win7 potplayer</p><h2 id="cl_1">1.威联通设置</h2><p itemprop="description">首先进入你威联通的管理页面</p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ar07k96x/pic_2/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202011/20/5fb72940a2a8b66.png_e680.jpg" title="" alt="进入控制台"/></a>进入控制台</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ar07k96x/pic_3/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202011/20/5fb729409c1b59605.png_e680.jpg" title="" alt="选择web服务器"/></a>选择web服务器</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ar07k96x/pic_4/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202011/20/5fb7294098123929.png_e680.jpg" title="" alt="选择webdav"/></a>选择webdav</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ar07k96x/pic_5/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202011/20/5fb729410cebe1719.png_e680.jpg" title="" alt="启用并设置专用端口不要和之前设置过的端口重复"/></a>启用并设置专用端口不要和之前设置过的端口重复</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ar07k96x/pic_6/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202011/20/5fb72941083266601.png_e680.jpg" title="" alt="设置webdav访问共享文件夹权限"/></a>设置webdav访问共享文件夹权限</span>